snippet.description:
The upcoming sequence on the show will involve the Roadies, taking on a particularly perilous task that will test their mettle and determination. This task is poised to be a true test of their abilities and resilience.

Following the completion of this task, the attention will shift to the Gang Leaders, who will engage in a strategic and suspenseful game of poker. This card game will serve as the means by which the allocation of immunity will be decided. Each Gang Leader's ability to strategize and make calculated moves will play a significant role in determining which Roadie will ultimately be granted immunity from elimination.

Once the poker game concludes and the outcome is established, the focus will return to the Roadies as they make their way to the campsite. However, what was meant to be a moment of rest and respite takes a dramatic turn as a heated and intense argument unfolds between two prominent figures among the Roadies, Piyu and Bhoomika. The exchange of verbal volleys and strong emotions creates a tense atmosphere, drawing the attention of everyone present and underscoring the underlying tensions that can arise within a competitive and high-pressure environment.
